      • selectedPdscDoc

        private static PDSCDocument selectedPdscDoc
        contains always current selected form with and all necessary information on which user is working. On This variable are based many function like "save file" in Menu , ecc ecc. IMPORTANT : set to null before creation of new xmlForm, and after creation update it; This is the only way the tagCustomizationFrameListener has to distinguish creation of new xmlForm from the update of selected form; selectedForm change based on current selected tab in wizardFrame
